lines.text: What's wrong with you? Your eyes? You need glasses?

lines.character: Eddie Williams aka Don Sebastian II

lines.text:
[after Rosalie drops the key down her dress]
...the key to the whole situation somewhere between Tijuana and the border!
lines.character: Eddie Williams aka Don Sebastian II

lines.text: Are you going to Mexico to live?
Yes - if I don't go to Mexico, I won't live.
lines.character: Eddie Williams aka Don Sebastian II

lines.text: I was gonna tell you the one about my uncle. He fell down the well. You know what happened? He kicked the bucket.
lines.character: Eddie Williams aka Don Sebastian II
